to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"its own previous Olympic record\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"3:29.69\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States were second at the Paris La Defense Arena in 3:30.20 and China third in 3:30.30.\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 421, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9691915408848144, \"rank\": 0.01655773383959491, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9371832758730723, \"rank\": 0.04985671998010881, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"3:30.20\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"3:30.30\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me it's definitely about getting up there and doing my country proud,\\\" said Jack, who missed out on the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"Jack\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a really special moment to stand on the podium with the other three girls, and represent the other two girls from our heat swim, I am really proud of myself and how far I have come, but I definitely missed that opportunity in 2021.\\\"\", \"from\": 643